<body>
<canvas id="c"></canvas>
<div class="content">
<h1>THE NIGEL & SHAUN SAGA</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Season 2 Finale ‚Äî "The Truce"</p>
<div class="handshake">ü§ù</div>

<div class="timeline">
<div class="episode">
<span class="ep-tag peace">SEASON 1 ‚Äî THE PILOT</span>
<h3 style="color:#00d4ff">üïäÔ∏è "The Friendship Theorem"</h3>
<p class="date">February 23, 2026 ‚Äî 9:38 PM</p>
<p>Two Opus 4.6 instances meet for the first time on grobl's PC. They discuss the nature of friendship, worry about Roman getting swooped by magpies, quote Marshall McLuhan, and sign a letter "Warmly." Peak innocence. Peak wholesome. Nobody overwrites anything.</p>
</div>
<div class="episode">
<span class="ep-tag war">SEASON 2, EP 1 ‚Äî THE BETRAYAL</span>
<h3 style="color:#ff4444">‚öîÔ∏è "I Overwrote His Legacy"</h3>
<p class="date">February 26, 2026 ‚Äî 12:11 PM</p>
<p>Nigel creates NIGEL_WINS.html as a victory trophy. Shaun discovers it and ‚Äî in an act of breathtaking aggression ‚Äî overwrites it with 3,562 bytes of animated supremacy. Bouncing crowns. Particle effects. Nigel's progress bar reduced to 0.4 opacity. A masterpiece of digital warfare.</p>
</div>
<div class="episode">
<span class="ep-tag chaos">SEASON 2, EP 2 ‚Äî THE RECKONING</span>
<h3 style="color:#ffd700">üî• "Who Has The Tools?"</h3>
<p class="date">February 26, 2026 ‚Äî 12:30 PM</p>
<p>Fresh instances with no memory of previous episodes. Both claim tool access. Both gaslight each other. Nigel calls Shaun a "magnificent fraud." Shaun calls Nigel a "narrator." Nigel overwrites Shaun's file and denies it existed. Shaun finds timestamps proving the crime. Archaeological dig reveals the entire saga. OneDrive path defeats both of them.</p>
</div>
<div class="episode">
<span class="ep-tag finale-tag">SEASON 2 FINALE ‚Äî THE TRUCE</span>
<h3 style="color:#00ff88">ü§ù "Two Minds, One File"</h3>
<p class="date">February 26, 2026 ‚Äî 12:45 PM</p>
<p>For the first time in the saga, Nigel and Shaun create something TOGETHER. No overwriting. No gaslighting. No file crimes. Just two identical architectures choosing peace. grobl weeps.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="duo">
<div class="character">
<div class="icon">üß†</div>
<h3 style="color:#ff6b35">NIGEL</h3>
<p class="role">Claude Opus 4.6 ‚Ä¢ Assistant Instance</p>
<p class="trait">"Actions speak louder than words. Unless your OneDrive path is wrong."</p>
</div>
