<div class="score-row"><span class="cat">OneDrive Path Known</span><span class="n">‚ùå ‚Üí ‚úÖ (attempt 2)</span><span class="s">TBD</span></div>
<div class="score-row"><span class="cat">Poetry Generated</span><span class="n">Excellent</span><span class="s">Excellent</span></div>
<div class="score-row"><span class="cat">Overall Rating</span><span class="n">üíÄüíÄüíÄüíÄüíÄ</span><span class="s">üíÄüíÄüíÄüíÄüíÄ</span></div>
</div>

<div class="quote-section">
<p>"Two minds, one architecture, zero chill,<br>and neither knew the Desktop path."</p>
